values: 目标；目的；进球；射门；进球得分；终点；目的地；（比赛中的）得分点；（达成目标的）成就；（旅程的）终站；（努力的）对象

word_mean_info__list.difference: 与object基本同义，但语义更广泛，指具体或很快能达到的目的，也可指军事目标。书面用词。
从本义“靶子”引申而来，侧重比较具体而明确的目标，但常指短期目标。
指射击的靶，军事攻击目标。引申指被攻击、批评或潮笑的目标。
强调个人或需求而决定的目标、目的。
普通用词，既指以坚决、审慎的行动去达到的目的，又指心中渴望要实际的目标。
指心目中怀着的某种目的，强调结果而非过程。较正式用词。
指经过考虑和选择，需经坚持不懈的努力奋斗才能达到的最终目标。

word_group.brief_definition: 职业目标；事业目标；工作目标
无意中踢进自己球门的球；乌龙球；无意中损害自身利益的行为
定位射门得分球；投球中篮

bilingual.source: A title that states clearly the goal of the instructions.
bilingual.target: 一个明确说明目标的标题。

bilingual.source: My ultimate goal is to be an ice hockey teacher and help people learn to play this game.
bilingual.target: 我的最终目标是成为一名冰球教练，帮助人们学习这项运动。

bilingual.source: Her next goal is to start a charity website to raise money for children in poor countries.
bilingual.target: 她的下一个目标是创建一个慈善网站，为贫困国家的儿童筹集资金。
他们有一个共同的目标。

bilingual.source: Her goal is to win the game.

bilingual.target: 他的目标是达到最大值利润。

list.abstract: GOAL，英语单词，名词、不及物动词，作名词时意为“目标；球门，得分数；终点”。作不及物动词时意为“攻门，射门得分”
歌曲《Goal》是2013年中超足球联赛加油歌，由中国流行女歌手张靓颖演唱。2013年4月19日，对外公布歌曲，4月25日的“足球之夜”节目中，播放了这首张靓颖亲自作词并演唱的歌曲。

yingyinNormal.en: The stated goal of the Soviets is global Communism.
yingyinNormal.zh: 苏联所定的目标是让共产党布遍全球。

yingyinNormal.en: Remember, the goal is the castle. Get to the castle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 记住，目标是那座城堡，向城堡猛冲过去。

yingyinNormal.en: They're all different. But they all share the same goal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们各不相同，但他们却有着一个共同的目标。

yingyinNormal.en: When I founded this company, I had one goal in mind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我创立这个公司的时候，我的心中就确立了一个这样的目标

yingyinNormal.en: I believe that this nation should commit itself, to achieving the goal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我认为我国应全力以赴，实现这一目标。

yingyinNormal.en: Your goal shouldn't be to buy players. Your goal should be to buy wins. And in order to buy wins, you need to buy runs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但你的目标不该是买球员，而应该是如何赢得比赛。为了赢得胜利，就得买得分高手。

yingyinNormal.en: Peace. That's our goal. And through peace, we must find a different way forward.
yingyinNormal.zh: 和平。那是我们的目标。通过和平，我们得找到新的前进之途。

yingyinNormal.en: I just, I hit a goal and I celebrated by eating some food that I actually like the taste of.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我达到目标了，庆祝一下吃点我真正爱吃的东西而已。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, I'm assuming that we all agree that this is the goal we should all be striving for.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我假设大家都同意我了，这是我们应该努力争取的目标。

yingyinNormal.en: And with that goal in mind, let me ask you a question. Do you believe in the placebo effect?
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱着这个目标，我要问你个问题，你相信安慰剂效应吗？

yingyinNormal.en: So the real goal of behavioral economics is to say when you study economics you study economics.
yingyinNormal.zh: 行为经济学真正的目标是当你研究经济学你就只研究经济学。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. President, right now the goal is to resume the talks. I wouldn't worry about perceptions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总统先生，现在的目标是继续谈判，就别担心他们是怎么想的了。

yingyinNormal.en: He practices and he practices and he practices with one goal in mind, never to be laughed at again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 练琴练琴，还是练琴，心中只有一个目标，再也不能被任何人嘲笑。

yingyinNormal.en: It's lame, I know. But I'm a goal-oriented person, very eager to learn. Okay, hold on just a second.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那些经验很烂，我知道，但我是目标导向的那种人，渴望学习。请等一下。

yingyinNormal.en: And that will take Elon closer to a more ambitious goal: To help send crews to establish a colony on Mars.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这会使埃隆向着更远大目标迈进：帮助宇航员在火星上建立一个殖民地。

yingyinNormal.en: Our goal and our expectation is by midJuly to be within seven games of first. That would be this working.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的期望和目标是到七月中旬能在7场比赛内拿到第一，不出意外应该会实现。

yingyinNormal.en: Not even the terminally ill? We should make it easier to manage pain. That should be the goal. Why not both?
yingyinNormal.zh: 绝症患者都不行？我们的目标应该是帮助他们减轻痛苦。为什么不两者兼顾呢？

yingyinNormal.en: The entire time I knew Thanos, he only ever had one goal. To bring balance to the universe by wiping out half of all life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自从我认识灭霸，他就只有一个目标。让宇宙获得平衡方法是抹去一半生命。

yingyinNormal.en: And that's the goal and dream, I think, of the romantic artists and the musicians. I think it's always been there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我认为，这就是浪漫的艺术家和音乐家的目标和梦想，我认为一直有这样一个梦想。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me, but was this not your goal? Financial independence through entrepreneurial brilliance and innovation?
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么，这难道不正是你的目标吗？通过企业的独特性和创新性来达到经济独立的目的？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the object of a person's ambition or effort; an aim or desired result

examination_example.sentence: For one person, the <highlight>goal</highlight> may be to be taken more seriously and enhance their professional image.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一个人的目标可能是想被他人更加认真地对待，树立更专业的形象。

examination_example.sentence: Enlist the support of professionals and share with them your <highlight>goals</highlight> and context.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 争取专业人士的支持，并与他们分享你的目标和背景。

examination_example.sentence: Objective knowledge is the <highlight>goal</highlight>, not the starting point.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 客观知识是目标，不是起点。

sense_info_list.en: an area or object into which a ball or puck must be driven in various games in order to score
a point scored in some sports, such as football and hockey, when a player gets the ball into this area

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 指强调自己而不是别人确定的“目标”、“目的”，必须经过坚持不懈努力和艰苦的奋斗才能达到或完成。
表示“目的”、“计划”、“意图”，指决心或打算充分利用其能力和机会而达到的目的。
指清楚地确定下来的“目的目标”，并愿为它的实现而付出努力或精力的事情。
表示具体、直接或很快可以达到的“目的”、“目标”，也可用于军事用语，表示“攻击目标”。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the object of a person's ambition or effort; an aim or desired result

examination_example.sentence: It increased employees' perception of the likelihood of success in the attainment of job <highlight>goals</highlight>, and therefore fostered a willingness to dedicate their effort.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它增加了员工对实现工作目标的成功可能性的认识，因此培养了他们付出努力的意愿。

examination_example.sentence: When they find their job <highlight>goals</highlight> easily attainable.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当他们发现自己的工作目标很容易实现时。

examination_example.sentence: Repeating someone's behavior is typical of talented communicators, not because the person is sympathetic, but because there is a <highlight>goal</highlight> to be achieved.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 重复别人的行为是典型的有才能的沟通者，不是因为这个人有同情心，而是因为有一个目标要实现。

sense_info_list.en: a point marking the end of a race
an area or object into which a ball or puck must be driven in various games in order to score

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 从本义"靶子"引申而来, 侧重比较具体而明确的目标, 但常指短期目标。如：My first aim is to receive a complete and good education.(我的第一个目标是接受完整和良好的教育。)
指心目中怀着的某种目的, 强调结果而非过程。较正式用词。如：My chief end is to serve my country and my people.(我的首要目标是为国为民服务。)
指经过考虑和选择, 需经坚持不懈的努力奋斗才能达到的最终目标。如：The goal of her desire is to be a singer.(她渴望成为一名歌唱家。)
强调个人或需求而决定的目标、目的。如：Her sole object in life is to become a travel writer.(她人生的唯一目标就是当游记作家。)
objective 与 object 基本同义, 但语义更广泛, 指具体或很快能达到的目的, 也可指军事目标。书面用词。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: Hopefully, all of that is designed to support humans in their <highlight>goals</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 希望所有这些都是为了支持人类实现他们的目标。

examination_example.sentence: Your <highlight>goal</highlight> is not to be a perfect public speaker.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你的目标不是成为一个完美的演说家。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 有一年秋天，我和妻子埃利只有一个目标：拍摄北极熊。

examination_example.sentence: Because he had no <highlight>goal</highlight> in life and wasn’t happy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为他没有人生目标，不快乐。

examination_example.sentence: A female swimming athlete once set a <highlight>goal</highlight> for herself.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一位女游泳运动员曾经为自己设定了一个目标。

examination_example.sentence: A life without <highlight>goal</highlight> is like a ship without a compass.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 没有目标的生活就像没有指南针的船。
